window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Wedding bells toll disaster.</b><br> <br> Ellesworth's resident amateur sleuth is about to tie the knot, but what should be a happy time is marred by a new case to solve. Brides-to-be are under attack, turning up dead missing their left ring fingers. Heartbreak is a powerful motivator and the longer Kalina searches the clearer it becomes that their killer is a scorned lover.<br> <br> Will Kalina solve the series of grisly deaths before the killer finds their ultimate target?</p> <p><i>HAVE AND HOLD is the fourth book in this quirky, fast-paced cozy mystery series where you'll find a dash of nerdy fun mixed with your new favorite amateur sleuth.</i></p> <p><b><i>Buy HAVE AND HOLD to save the brides today!</i></b></p>"; 
